
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head>
	<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
	<title>Newsletter Title</title>
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/screen.css" type="text/css"/>
</head>

<body topmargin="0" leftmargin="0" marginheight="0" marginwidth="0" style="-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased; width:100% !important; -webkit-text-size-adjust:none; margin: 0; padding: 0;">

	

	<!-- Layout 1 -->
	<!-- Generic Content - 1 column text only -->
	<repeater>
		<layout label="Generic Article">
			<table class="w640 article" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" align="center">

				<!-- Section Divider -->
				<tr>
					<td class="w640" width="640" height="18" align="center"></td>
				</tr>
				<tr>
					<td class="w640 section-divider" width="100%">
						<table class="w640" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" align="center">
							<tr>
								<td class="w20 hide" width="20"></td>
								<td class="w640 grey" width="600" height="1"></td>
								<td class="w20 hide" width="20"></td>
							</tr>
						</table>
					</td>
				</tr>
				<tr>
					<td class="w640" width="640" height="24" align="center"></td>
				</tr>

				<!-- Content -->
				<tr>
					<td class="w640 section-content" width="100%">
						<table class="w640 article-content" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" align="center">
							<tr>
								<td class="w20 hide" width="20"></td>
								<td class="w640 article-copy" width="600">
									<h1><singleline label="Article Title" repeatertitle="true"><a href="#">Recordatorio de Cita Virtual</a></singleline></h1>
									<multiline label="Main Article Content">
										<p>Tienes una evento programado con <b>{{event.professional.user.name}} {{event.professional.user.surname}}</b>.</p>
										<ul>
											<li>Inicio de la consulta: {{ event.getStartDate()|date('d-M-Y: H:i') }}</li>
										</ul>
										<p>Puedes acceder a la consulta mediante el link que te proporcionamos a continuaci√≥n:<br> 
										<a href="http://{{host}}{{path('home_guess_client',{token:event.getClientAccessToken()}) }}">http://{{host}}{{path('home_guess_client',{token:event.getClientAccessToken()}) }}</a>
										</p>

									</multiline>
								</td>
								<td class="w20 hide" width="20"></td>
							</tr>
						</table>
					</td>
				</tr>

				<!-- Button -->
				<tr>
					<td class="w640" width="100%">
						<table class="w640 article-content" width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" align="center">
							<tr>
								<td class="w640" width="200" height="30" valign="middle" align="center">
									<p class="btn">
										<singleline label="Click-through Link">Acceder a la Consulta</singleline>
									</p>
								</td>
								<td class="w20 hide" width="420"></td>
							</tr>
						</table>
					</td>
				</tr>

			</table>
		</layout>

		
	</repeater>


	</body>
</html>
